On the second of December the noose closes, and the schoolteacher of Atoyac enters the corridos. The reasoning for distance is sound and the sound of it carries. Some of the descended are taken at the bus stations; some reach the Liga, which welcomes anything that still angers; a few simply vanish into day labor and silence, carrying their verdict with them. The Party's doors stayed clean. In Guerrero, clean doors have a particular reputation.
